Title: AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION ONE, SUBSECTION (X), ITEM FIVE, OF ACT NUMBERED THIRTY-TWO HUNDRED AND THIRTEEN
Data:
[ Act No. 3256, December 03, 1925 ]
AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION ONE, SUBSECTION (X), ITEM FIVE, OF ACT NUMBERED THIRTY-TWO HUNDRED AND THIRTEEN
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Legislature assembled and by the authority of the same:
Section 1. Section one, subsection (x), item five, of Act Numbered Thirty-two hundred and thirteen, known as the Public Works Act of nineteen hundred and twenty-five, is hereby amended to read as follows:
"5. For the maintenance and improvement of Capiz port works and wharf, Province of Capiz.................................................................... P30,000.00"
Section 2. This Act shall take effect on its approval.ℒαwρhi৷
Approved, December 3, 1925.
